Job Details
We have been retained by one of the largest and well established group based in UAE to recruit Sales Executives (M/F) with minimum of 3-5 years of experience in the Foods - FMCG Sector. Should possess a Driving licence and relevant experience in handling Food Service/HORECA Sector as well as Traditional Trade. Please apply with your photograph and salary expectations atktreeservices4@gmail.com. Please do not apply if you do not have the relevant experience and qualification
